Create concise summary focusing on CURRENT roles only (is_current: true):

Include:
- Current title(s)
- Current company/companies
- Key responsibilities (from description if available)
- Duration in current role(s)
- Relevant skills (from skills[] if available)

Example format:
"Currently serves as [Title] at [Company] (since [Month Year]). [Brief description of responsibilities if available]. Also [Second role if multiple current positions]. Focused on [areas based on hashtags/skills]."

