## USER PROMPT

Analyze this LinkedIn person profile data to determine how well this contact matches our Ideal Customer Profile.

Using the artifacts available to you:
- Buyer_Personas.md (target roles and personas)
- ICP_Profile.md (target company characteristics)
- Company_Description.md (our offering and value proposition)

Focus on:
1. Current job title and seniority (from experience where is_current: true)
2. Company context (from current_company and company info)
3. Profile quality and professional presence (followers, connections, creator status)
4. Decision-making signals (from title, description, career progression)
5. Geographic location (match to ICP_Profile.md markets)

Handle multiple current roles appropriately (score based on highest-ranking role).
Handle missing or null data gracefully.
Note if profile is incomplete or missing critical information.

Return your analysis as valid JSON using the exact schema provided in the system prompt.

